data.description: Great yard, great house, great neighborhood.  This 3 bed 2 bath home is loaded with charm and features that draw you in.  The concrete patio in the back beckons you on those warm summer nights.  "Grill with me, relax with me, forget about your troubles."  The house exterior absolutely pops and the huge yard   with its bold greens and colorful trees dance with your senses.  The home is well maintained with copioius spaces left to finish should you need more sq ft.  Man caves, she sheds, and more are just waiting for you to bring your own touches.
